
  Usage is:
    entrypoint.py <instance> <option>
      <instance> = case sensitive instasnce name to filter out.
      <option>   = case sensitive options listed above.
      
          Data:
            --iname:                VRRP instance name
            --dont-track-primary:   Ignore VRRP interface faults.
            --skip-check-adv-addr:  Checking all the addresses in a received VRRP advert.
            --stric-mode            VRRPv3 strict mode
            --last-transition:      Last state transition.

          Stats:
            --become-master:        Is the current node in Master state?
                                      0 = False
                                      1 = True
  Example:
    ./entrypoint.py VI_1 --become-master
